manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Perfect for Baby Led Weaning Our chewable spoons are thoughtfully designed for babies who are not yet adept at using utensils, or at an earlier point where they're not even aware of the concept that they can actually feed themselves. Getting little hands used to utensils can be a little daunting, but not anymore. With our spoons, learning is simply turned into a breeze and a lot more fun!

It Can't Be Any Easier to Use Every single part of our spoons is tailored to babies' needs, and thus caters to their interests. Coming as a perfect combo of a Teether and a Utensil, our smart spoon will keep your baby happily occupied for hours, while simultaneously helping him or her master how to use utensils, inadvertently and effortlessly! Perfect for the first stage of self feeding, and all the way up to older babies and toddlers.

No Choking Hazard Our spoons give you peace of mind with a built-in Choke Barrier in the middle, which is designed to prevent babies from shoving the spoons too far into their mouths. Super Easy to Hold Featuring non-slip silicone and textured surface, our rounded handle fits little hands just right and it feels super nice to the touch. Chewable and Durable Most babies start self-feeding at a time when they're still teething, that's why your baby will love chewing on those sensory bumps on the back of the spoon heads!

Great Gift Idea This set of chewable spoons is a great gift to wow your loved ones, not just for Baby Shower but on any other occasion that matters. Apart from spoons, we also have a wide variety of feeding supplies for you to choose from - and each is a unique gift, too!

Made of Safer Material For SAMiGO, safety is always our top priority. Rest assured our spoons are made of Food Grade Silicone and thus free of BPA, PVC, Lead and Phthalate. Cleaning Is a Breeze Hand wash with warm, soapy water, or just throw on the top rack of your dishwasher and let it do the rest. Plus, it’s also microwave, fridge and freezer safe. For Your Child's Safety Remove packaging before giving to your child. Inspect before each use and discard at the first sign of weakness or damage. Always use this product under adult supervision.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect for Beginners
reviews.reviewText: I recently got these spoons for my little one when she started eating solids and wanted to use the utensils herself. They’re the perfect fit for her to use as they aren’t as long as some of the other spoons we’ve tried. I’m also loving the fact that they came in a pack of 3, perfect for her to hold one when she’s using the other to actually eat. I say you get your money’s worth out of this pack as they’re cute colors, and versatile (she loves them as a teether, too!). Great value for the money.
